high_descs: Move to the sink to your right.
Pick up the blue plate next right of the sink.
Bring the plate to the microwave over the stove, behind you to your left.
Put the plate in the microwave and heat it.
Take the heated plate to the counter, left of the stove.
Put the plate on the counter left of the stove.
